title: Lose Yourself (in the team)
description:
Swagu and Perk discuss the culture of the Nets and why James Harden wanted out, how Aaron Donald dominated when it mattered most, why they're happy for Odell Beckham, Jr., as well as their thoughts on the Super Bowl halftime show. Let's get it!
